<h2>About Us</h2>
<p class="gold-italic-glow">
    <strong>All Hands on Deck</strong>Is a modern staffing and consulting company that was founded with a clear idea:
    to make it easier for companies to find the right skills – and for people to find the right workplace.
    We work closely with both customers and consultants and build long-term relationships where security, flexibility and quality
    are always at the center.
</p>

<p class="gold-italic-glow">
    We specialize in <strong>Industry, Warehouse, Production, Technology and Service</strong>, but also help companies
    in other industries that need fast and reliable staffing. Our network consists of engaged employees who
    are used to taking responsibility, working shifts and quickly getting familiar with new work environments.
</p>

<p class="gold-italic-glow">
    What sets us apart from other staffing companies is our philosophy:
    <strong>The right person in the right place – every time.</strong>
    We place great emphasis on personality, work ethic and matchmaking, not just CV and experience.
    That's why our clients can trust that they will get staff who work in practice, not just on paper.
</p>

<p class ="gold-italic-glow">
    For our consultants, we offer secure employment, fair conditions and the opportunity to develop in their professional role.
    We believe that people grow when they are given the right conditions – and when they feel that someone actually cares.
</p>

<p class="gold-italic-glow">
    <strong>All Hands on Deck</strong> is the obvious choice for companies that want a flexible, fast and professional staffing partner.
    And for those of you looking for new opportunities in working life, we are a safe harbor to drop anchor in.
</p>